hello: WHTCORPS is an embedded, cloud-native, fault-tolerant, distributed computing and information systems architecture for IoT, Data Centers, and Nanotechnology
subline: Beyond Infrastructure as a service: WHTCORPS offers consistent rna-seq workflows, post-quantum encryption for wearables; Automated Machine Learning Pipelines for Chaos Engineering, and everything in between.
aboutProject: WHTCORPS aims to bring BSD to the new millenium via ASICS, Embedded FPGA, and Lab-on-a-Chip to help solve humanity's biggest problems.
